		"description": "# **Learning App API Documentation**\n\nBase URL:\n\n``` json\n{{baseURL}}  (Default: http://localhost:8080)\n\n ```\n\nAuthentication:\n\n- Uses **Bearer Token** (`Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}`)\n    \n- Obtain token via **Login API**\n    \n\n---\n\n## **Health Check**\n\n### `GET /health`\n\nCheck if the API server is running.  \n**Auth Required:** Yes  \n**Response:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"status\": \"OK\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## **Auth & User Management**\n\n### **Register User**\n\n`POST /user/signup`\n\nRegisters a new user (Student or Instructor).  \n**Body:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"firstName\": \"instructor\",\n  \"lastName\": \"instructor\",\n  \"contact\": \"0712150138\",\n  \"email\": \"instructor@gmail.com\",\n  \"role\": \"689ad8ac81797dc972c845ca\", \n  \"password\": \"instructor123\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Response:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"User registered successfully\",\n  \"user\": { ... }\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n### **Login**\n\n`POST /user/login`\n\nLogs in a Student or Instructor and returns a JWT token.\n\n**Student Login Example:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"email\": \"student@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"student123\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Instructor Login Example:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"email\": \"instructor@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"instructor123\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Response:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"token\": \"JWT_TOKEN_HERE\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": \"...\",\n    \"role\": \"student\"\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n### **Add Role**\n\n`POST /role`\n\nCreate a new role (e.g., Student, Instructor).\n\n**Body:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"roleName\": \"student\",\n  \"roleDescription\": \"Student\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Auth Required:** Yes (Admin or privileged user)\n\n---\n\n## **Course Management**\n\n### **Create Course**\n\n`POST /course`\n\nCreates a new course.\n\n**Body:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"title\": \"course 01\",\n  \"description\": \"course 01 description\",\n  \"duration\": 3,\n  \"content\": \"course 01 content\",\n  \"instructor\": \"689ad8b781797dc972c845cd\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Auth Required:** Yes (Instructor)\n\n---\n\n### **Delete Course**\n\n`DELETE /course/:courseId`\n\nDeletes a specific course.\n\n**Auth Required:** Yes (Instructor who owns the course or Admin)\n\n---\n\n### **Get All Courses**\n\n`GET /course`\n\nFetches all available courses.  \n**Auth Required:** Yes  \n**Response:**\n\n``` json\n[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"course 01\",\n    \"description\": \"course 01 description\",\n    ...\n  }\n]\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n### **Get Courses by Instructor (Token)**\n\n`GET /course/instructor`\n\nFetches courses for the authenticated instructor.  \n**Auth Required:** Yes (Instructor)\n\n---\n\n### **Get Courses by Instructor ID**\n\n`GET /course/instructor/:instructorId`\n\nFetches courses for a specific instructor ID.  \n**Auth Required:** Yes\n\nExample:\n\n``` json\n/course/instructor/689ad8b781797dc972c845cd\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## **Environment Variables**\n\n- `baseURL` → API base URL (default: `http://localhost:8080`)\n    \n- `authToken` → JWT token (set after login)",
